  <notes>
    The three entry points represent:
    1. IndexFileAsync - User-initiated via API, uses OBO for file download
    2. IndexFileAppOnlyAsync - Background job, downloads file with app-only auth
    3. IndexContentAsync - Optimization when text is already extracted

    All three should produce identical indexed content for the same source file.
  </notes>

